sourcesContent: // 1) Import the React and ReactDOM librariesimport React from "react";import ReactDOM from "react-dom/client";import App from  './App';import Style from './style.css';// 2) Get a references to the div with ID rootconst el = document.getElementById('root');// 3) Tell React to take control of that elementconst root = ReactDOM.createRoot(el)// 4) Show the component on the screenroot.render(<App/>);
